      "dialogue": "You stuck with new concepts and more advanced problems than the ones we've seen before. Think back to your work with eighths. Together, we built a strategy: [event:690292c6d36d03c4] halving, then halving again, then halving once more. That's how math experts approach complex problems - breaking them into manageable steps.",
