        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Step",
      "dialogue": "You've also learned that[event:690d22170f7e126c]  fractions do more than represent parts of shapes - they’re also numbers with exact positions on a number line. And you worked out [event:690d24334040c1b3]that bigger denominators create smaller intervals. Every fraction has its own place on that number line.",
